        <item>
          <title>Nvidia Shares Plummet After Tighter US Controls on AI Chip Exports</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Shares in computer chip makers slumped early Wednesday after Nvidia announced tighter US government controls on exports of computer chips used for artificial intelligence, citing risks that the products 'may be used in or diverted to' a supercomputer in China.]]></description>
